1
00:00:00,280 --> 00:00:01,919
One day, the organization took me

2
00:00:04,559 --> 00:00:09,439
Abu Seif came to me. The first time, he came with Abu Khaled al-Idlibi and other men

3
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:13,000
They took me away

4
00:00:14,279 --> 00:00:17,239
They said, “Come with us to carry out your sentence”

5
00:00:20,600 --> 00:00:21,600
Of course

6
00:00:22,839 --> 00:00:25,519
They took me along with six other men

7
00:00:28,839 --> 00:00:32,439
Among them was a man named Abdul Karim al-Ghaffaf

8
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:34,200
He was from the al-Marandi clan

9
00:00:35,920 --> 00:00:40,759
He was one of my uncles, and his charge was adopting Shia beliefs

10
00:00:42,359 --> 00:00:44,600
An old man, about 80 years old

11
00:00:45,200 --> 00:00:48,600
There was also another man from the al-Bu Assaf clan named Yasin al-Yasin

12
00:00:48,600 --> 00:00:49,600
Anyway

13
00:00:50,399 --> 00:00:51,840
There were six men, and I was the seventh

14
00:00:52,560 --> 00:00:57,600
They took me in a car, and I felt that we had left the city

15
00:01:04,599 --> 00:01:08,879
They made us get out, and there was a cool breeze in the air

16
00:01:09,239 --> 00:01:11,840
They made us kneel on our knees

17
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,879
And when they made us kneel

18
00:01:17,040 --> 00:01:19,920
One of the emirs said, “Remove the cloth blindfold from Talal al-Shuweimi’s eyes”

19
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:23,439
They removed the blindfold from my eyes

20
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:30,400
Then I looked to my right and left and saw that everyone was lined up on both sides

21
00:01:31,719 --> 00:01:35,120
They told them, “You did this and that, say the two testimonies”

22
00:01:37,519 --> 00:01:42,480
So they recited the testimonies, and each one was shot in the head

23
00:01:43,239 --> 00:01:48,200
I looked around and the place was full of trees,it used to be a Baath Pioneers camp

24
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:54,719
When we were kids, we used to go there in summer for school camps during the Assad regime

25
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:58,879
One of them said to me, “Talal al-Shuweimi”

26
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:03,599
What do you want?

27
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:07,959
I said, I don’t want anything. You brought me here and sentenced me to execution

28
00:02:10,879 --> 00:02:11,919
He said to me

29
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:17,599
They removed the cloth blindfold from my eyes so I could see around me

30
00:02:19,159 --> 00:02:25,439
Among them were well-known people,some of the senior figures in the ISIS state

31
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:31,719
High-ranking figures who are still alive today

32
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:37,800
He said to me

33
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:40,599
Now we’ll carry out the sentence and get rid of you

34
00:02:40,639 --> 00:02:42,080
Then another masked man came

35
00:02:44,919 --> 00:02:46,080
And said to me

36
00:02:48,879 --> 00:02:50,199
What is your last wish?

37
00:02:55,479 --> 00:02:56,479
At that moment

38
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:29,039
I told him, to speak with my children

39
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,919
He placed the pistol on my head

40
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:44,000
He said, “Say the two testimonies,” so I did

41
00:03:46,879 --> 00:03:47,879
Then he struck me

42
00:03:48,439 --> 00:03:52,800
As if he hit me in the head, but he fired the shot beside my ear

43
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:59,599
When he fired beside my ear, out of terror and horror

44
00:04:01,599 --> 00:04:04,120
My hands were tied behind my back, and I fell to the ground

45
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:07,479
From the terror of it,it was like an American movie

46
00:04:08,039 --> 00:04:09,159
I mean, something

47
00:04:09,599 --> 00:04:14,199
Something indescribable, something even the Jews wouldn’t envy you for

48
00:04:14,759 --> 00:04:21,800
Nor the Christians, nor Israel, nor even black devils would wish to see you in such a position

49
00:04:21,839 --> 00:04:23,519
They wouldn’t even gloat over you
